      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>Mia, Luis and Diego entered the back workshop of the garage.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>They saw Tomas having an argument with a boy who was sitting on a motorbike.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>"Look, Pablo" said Tomas, "That’s not your bike, and you can’t ride one anyhow, so get off."</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
   </paragraph>
   <paragraph>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The motorbike was on its rear stand in the middle of the workshop.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>Pablo shrugged his shoulders and said, "Look, that’s the front brake, that’s the clutch, that’s the gearbox and here’s the ignition."</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>Then he turned on the ignition and the engine started up.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
	   <sentence>
		   <text>CR</text>
		   <clip></clip>
	   </sentence>
	   <sentence>
		   <text>CR</text>
		   <clip></clip>
	   </sentence>
	   <sentence>
         <text>"Get off!" shouted Tomas.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
   </paragraph>
   <paragraph>
       <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>   
      <sentence>
         <text>"It’s easy!" yelled Pablo, over the engine noise.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>He suddenly gave a jerk, and hit the gearshift as the bike bumped forward off its stand.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>They all knew in a flash that Pablo meant to ride the bike out of the garage.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
   </paragraph>
   <paragraph>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The rear wheel of the bike came straight down on to a pool of oil.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The wheel spun around, and the bike slid to one side and then suddenly pulled away.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>It went straight at the corner of the garage.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The front wheel hit the leg of a bench and the bike bounced back before it lurched again.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>Then it fell over, throwing Pablo to one side.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>    
      </sentence>
   </paragraph>
   <paragraph>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>The engine stalled.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>All at once there was silence.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>Pablo got to his feet and scowled at the others.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>They were laughing so hard they couldn’t speak.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>He was red in the face and covered with blotches of oil and dirt.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>    
      </sentence>
   </paragraph>
